"form":"قُلْنا","in_corpus":true,"count":86,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"قُلْتُ","in_corpus":true,"count":2862,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نُقال","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أُقال","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أَقُول","in_corpus":true,"count":116,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نَقُول","in_corpus":true,"count":35,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"}],"frequency_in_corpus":7066,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"قالَ","root":"قول","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1618},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42874","n42933"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to say","examples":[{"text":"his Lord said to him: \"Bow (thy will to Me):\" He said: \"I bow (my will) to the Lord and Cherisher of the Universe.\""},{"text":"And when Abraham said, “My Lord, make this land safe, and spare me and my children from worshiping idols.”"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to call (by name)","examples":[{"text":"وَلَا تَقُولُوا لِمَن يُقْتَلُ فِي سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ أَمْوَاتٌ ۚ بَلْ أَحْيَاءٌ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تَشْعُرُونَ"},{"text":"قَالُوا سَمِعْنَا فَتًى يَذْكُرُهُمْ يُقَالُ لَهُ إِبْرَاهِيمُ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to tell","examples":[{"text":"قُلْ لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ يَغُضُّوا مِنْ أَبْصَارِهِمْ","english":"Tell the believing men to lower their gaze,..."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to advocate, to propound, to root, to stand up for, to support","examples":[{"text":"ويقول الأوروبيون بنوع خصوصي على الكفير وهو كذلك لبن شرقي يحضر في القوقاس بتخمير حليب البقر بخميرة خصوصية تباع في الصيدلات في أوروبا ومصر كتلا جامدة مرنة جلاتينية بيضاء مصفرة مستديرة أو مخروطية بحجم الحمصة. […]","english":"The Europeans advocate for a particular kind [of yoghurt] in consideration of kefir and it is likewise an Eastern milk afforded in the Caucasus by acidifying cow’s milk with particular yeast, sold in pharmacies in Europe and Egypt in congealed heaps, elastic, gelatineous, round or conic like a chickpea."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"To nap."},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"To do something at noon."},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"To cancel a contract or a promise."}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qaː.la/","/ʔaːl/","/ɡaːl/","/qaːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42874","headword_ar":"قَالَ","root":"qwl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":". The objective complement of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAl","text_ar":"قال"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maquwlu Alqawoli","text_ar":"مَقُولُ القَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", must be a complete proposition, or a word signifying at least one complete proposition, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaAmFA","text_ar":"كَلَامًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or a word signifying a command or the like; or a word significant of a sound, termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isomu SawotK","text_ar":"اـِسْمُ صَوْتٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": it may be a verb; but cannot be an inf. n., as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EibaAdapN","text_ar":"عِبَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Gr.) [This is what is meant where] it is said in the Keshsháf,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEibaAdapu","text_ar":"العِبَادَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA tuqaAlu","text_ar":"لا تُقَالُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Kull, p. 327.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla lahu","text_ar":"قَالَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaATaba lh","text_ar":"خَاطَبَ له"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAl Eanohu","text_ar":"قال عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaY Enh","text_ar":"رَوَى عنه"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAl Ealayohi","text_ar":"قال عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotaraY","text_ar":"اِفْتَرَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh","text_ar":"عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAl bihi","text_ar":"قال بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hakama bh","text_ar":"حَكَمَ به"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAl fyh","text_ar":"قال فيه"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aijotahada fiyhi","text_ar":"اِجْتَهَدَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Marg. note in Additions to a copy of the KT.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla fiyhi famaA At~araka","text_ar":"قَالَ فِيهِ فَمَا اتَّرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aijotahada fiyhi","text_ar":"اِجْتَهَدَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraka","text_ar":"تَرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla Ealayohi","text_ar":"قَالَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said what was false, against him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tlw","text_ar":"تلو"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaw~ala","text_ar":"تَقَوَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla fiyhi","text_ar":"قَالَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanohu","text_ar":"عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"such a thing. ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla bika*aA","text_ar":"قَالَ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He asserted his belief in such"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2995},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a doctrine or the like: a well-known meaning. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAlati AlEayonaAni","text_ar":"قَالَتِ العَيْنَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eyes made a sign"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though saying...]. (TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla biraA^osihi","text_ar":"قَالَ بِرَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made a sign with his head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a motion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham, p. 242.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla biyadihi","text_ar":"قَالَ بِيَدِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla birijolihi","text_ar":"قَالَ بِرِجْلِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He walked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"struck"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla bivawobihi","text_ar":"قَالَ بِثَوْبِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his garment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla biAlmaA='i EalaY yadihi","text_ar":"قَالَ بِالمَا=ءِ عَلَى يَدِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He poured the water on his arm"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla fiyhi","text_ar":"قَالَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke against him; vituperated him."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla $iEorFA","text_ar":"قَالَ شِعْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"lit.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spoke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave utterance to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recited, poetry; he spoke in verse; he poetized,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"versified."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla","text_ar":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made a sign;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awomaA^a","text_ar":"اَوْمَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham, p. 601, where see other meanings: see also p. 242 of the same: and see Mgh.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla biyadihi","text_ar":"قَالَ بِيَدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made a sign with his hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning to say...]. (A trad. cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaT~a","text_ar":"حَطَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and another voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~afa","text_ar":"حَرَّفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"upon a thing. (Mgh.) See an ex. voce."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oraba","text_ar":"اَشْرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n42933","headword_ar":"قَالَ","root":"qyl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slept during midday:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stayed during midday."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hjr","text_ar":"هجر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qay~ala","text_ar":"قَيَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see another meaning, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bay~ata","text_ar":"بَيَّتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Mgh"]}]}}